name: Exclusive Power Women Tee
description:
The mission of the Power Woman Campaign is to create a worldwide awareness of women empowerment through social media networking,community outreach and special events. Get your tee and participate in the movement today!   

20% of all sales will go to the "Little Miss Power Woman" scholarship. The scholarship will help 2 graduating high school seniors apply a college of their choice as well as a book stipend for their first year. 

For more info please on the campaign and scholarship contact us at:
brandingbar@gmail.com
&
Follow The Power Women Campaign on twitter
@ThePowerWomen

name: Personalized Power Women Tee
description:
This campaign was created to show empowerment of women following other women via Twitter. Follow us @ThePowerWomen and get your name added to the back of the shirt today!

We encourage you to nominate other #powerwomen for us to follow! Let the world know you support the movement and have them follow via Twitter and in the real world! 

****Please RSVP your twitter name to insure it will be placed on the back at brandingbar@gmail.com****

Lets keep it going #Powerwomen!!!
